Description of incident: "After we have made and continue to make significant investments in technology and security, on August 22, we became aware that we were the victim of an unauthorized and unlawful access to our online hunting and fishing licensing applications in Idaho, Oregon and Washington."The information compromised included names, addresses, dates of birth, driver's license number, Social Security number. More Information: https://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-63929
